    "description": "Skala is a game about changing the physical scale of things. You can make yourself large enough to step over a giant cliff, or make a key small enough to be passed through a solid wall. The game explores the consequences of this rescaling mechanic through simple yet difficult puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884990/extras/821dcb99c4631798090435b015c45aa6.poster.avif?t=1720814990\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884990/extras/821dcb99c4631798090435b015c45aa6.webm?t=1720814990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884990/extras/821dcb99c4631798090435b015c45aa6.mp4?t=1720814990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>A level where you have to stretch yourself in order to reach a star.</i><br><br>Skala takes place in a graphically simple world with a big house and a star filled sky to explore. The world is covered by a relaxing soundtrack which let's you take in all of the games mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884990/extras/510ece35d19dc1c84be773418084b80e.avif?t=1720814990\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>There are over 70 puzzle levels to play through. Every level is unique and has some purpose, whether it's  introducing a new idea/mechanic, or developing on the concepts of previous levels.",
